!! # Noun inflection

!! Nouns in ERZYA inflect for number, case and declension (definite, indefinite and possessive).

!Problems
!LEXICON N-COLL_
!+Coll+Pl+Nom+Indef: #;
!LEXICON N-COM_
!+SP+Com+Indef: #;

!Defective paradigms
LEXICON N_PELE !!= @CODE@ РҝРөР»Рө:РҝРөР»СҢ, Р°Р»Рҫ:Р°Р»
+Relat+Abl:%>{РҙСӮ}Рһ1 K ;
+Relat+Loc:%>{РҫРөСҚГҳ} K ;
+Relat+Prl:%>Р“2Р° K ;
+Orth/PhonDeriv+Loc+Der+Der/cje+Pron:%>СҶРө N2_DEF_DECLENSION_KUDO ;
+Der+Der/ks:%>РәСҒ N_LEVKS ;
+Relat+Lat:%>{РҫРөСҚГҳ}РІ K ;

LEXICON VOCATIVE_
+Voc: ENDLEX ;

LEXICON VOCATIVE_J
+Voc:%>Р№ ENDLEX ;

LEXICON VOCATIVE_KAJ
+Voc:%>РәР°Р№ ENDLEX ;

!LEXICON VOCATIVE_SG_NOM_PXSG3
!+Sg+Nom+PxSg3: ENDLEX ;



!! ## KINSHIP 

!LEXICON N-KIN_KAL
