+Use/-Spell+Sg+Prl+Def+Use/NG+Err/Orth+Dial/NW:%>Р“2Р°%>СҒСӮСҢ%> N2Dem-SE ; !!= * **@CODE@** _СҢ_ retension through double %>%>
+Use/-Spell+Sg+Cmpr+Def+Use/NG+Err/Orth+Dial/NW:%>{РҫРөСҚГҳ}СҲРәР°%>СҒСӮСҢ%> N2Dem-SE ; !!= * **@CODE@** _СҢ_ retension through double %>%>
+Use/-Spell+Sg+Abe+Def+Use/NG+Err/Orth+Dial/NW:%>РІСӮ{РҫРөСҚ}РјРһ1%>%>СҒСӮСҢ%> N2Dem-SE ; !!= * **@CODE@** _СҢ_ retension through double %>%>
