! =================== !
! Inflectional lexica !
! =================== !

!
! Due to irregularity in spelling
! where triple consonants are disallowed
! and some double consonants are alternately dropped
! A two-class system has been extended to a six-classer
! _PANGO-N and Adj-chevte types are closed-class word sets
! which can drop their stem final vowels in certain combinations


! ================ !
! N-Def-Declension !
! ================ !

LEXICON N_KIT-Def-Declension
 SG_NOM_DEF ;
 SG-GEN-DEF ;
 SG-DAT-DEF ;
